questions.quote: So umm, you feel like taking a test? There's only one question.
Well I'm gonna be on it this year. I'm gonna be one of the party people.
So you have to tell Monica you don't want to have a baby right now?
Hey, have you seen Frank Jr., 'cause he's meeting me here with the triplets.
Barbara! Hi, how are you? Uh-huh. No, I understand. Yeah. Oh, oh, come on, no, I'm fine. Don't be silly. Yeah... oh, but you know, if-if anything else opens up, pleaHello? Hello?
Sure, yeah. I mean, it's Joey. I don't want him to get hurt. Well, I must say, I am on fire! First Chandler, now Joey!
Phoebe, you get the bear, uhm, Joey, you get the robot, and Chandler and I get the dog. Ok, and the race is going to go from here to here. Now the one who comes in last, stays!
